snippet.title: My Lovely Empress - Gameplay Trailer | TGS 2023
snippet.description:
Check out gameplay from My Lovely Empress, a empire management sim inspired by Asian mythology in whuch you must reap souls of your people in order to resurrect your deceased empress.
